# ERROR TIPS

### Extraction Errors
- Cannot extract from empty or non-existent containers
- Ensure the target chest contains the items you want to extract before attempting extraction

### Entity Status Issues
- Multiple burner mining drills are out of fuel - ensure continuous fuel supply to mining equipment
- Some inserters are waiting for source items - verify the supply chain is properly connected and supplied
- Some chests are full - implement better item management or increase storage capacity
- Boiler is out of fuel - maintain constant fuel supply for power generation

### Fluid System Issues
- Steam engine has no input liquid - ensure proper pipe connections and water flow
- Some pipe networks are empty - verify fluid connections and pump operations
